Name: Factorial CLI
Deliverable: CLI
Stack:
    Python
Guarantees:
    compute O(n)
    space O(1)
Behavior:
    Return the factorial of a given number
        Input:
            factorial to compute, as positional argument
        Output:
            Factorial value
        Transport:
            Stdout
        Errors:
            0: success
            1: input out of domain (negative value)
            2: invalid input (wrong argument count, non-integer...)
